BonfyreLedger — value accounting engine

  bonfyre-ledger assess <artifact.json>          detailed family report
  bonfyre-ledger assess-json <artifact.json>     JSON output
  bonfyre-ledger portfolio <root_dir>             full portfolio roll-up
  bonfyre-ledger delta <artifact.json>            value changes
  bonfyre-ledger export <root_dir> [--format json|csv]
